WEBVTT

00:01:55.456 --> 00:02:00.881
"So get some sage and burn it,

00:02:00.905 --> 00:02:03.403
and tell it to go away."

00:02:03.427 --> 00:02:07.089
So I said, "OK,"
and I went and I bought sage.

00:02:07.113 --> 00:02:11.174
I had never done this before,
so I set the sage on fire,

00:02:11.198 --> 00:02:17.898
waved it about, and said, "Go away!
This is my house! I live here.

00:02:17.922 --> 00:02:19.556
You don't live here!"

00:02:20.593 --> 00:02:23.874
But the feeling stayed.
Nothing got better.

00:02:23.898 --> 00:02:26.094
And then I started to think,

00:02:26.118 --> 00:02:28.890
OK, well now this thing is probably
just laughing at me,

00:02:28.914 --> 00:02:31.342
because it hasn't left,